US-003 is fully complete. All 5 artifact templates created in `fab/.kit/templates/` matching the TEMPLATES.md spec:

1. **proposal.md** — {CHANGE_NAME}, {DATE}, Why, What Changes, Affected Docs (New/Modified/Removed), Impact, Open Questions with [BLOCKING]/[DEFERRED] markers
2. **spec.md** — domain/topic sections, Requirement/Scenario format with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN, Deprecated Requirements, RFC 2119 keywords note
3. **plan.md** — Summary, Goals/Non-Goals, Technical Context, Research, Decisions (Why/Rejected), Risks/Trade-offs, File Changes (New/Modified/Deleted)
4. **tasks.md** — Phase structure, [P] parallel markers, sequential IDs (T001...), Execution Order section
5. **checklist.md** — CHK-* IDs, categories: Functional Completeness, Behavioral Correctness, Removal Verification, Scenario Coverage, Edge Cases, Security, Notes

All templates preserve HTML comment instructions and use `{CURLY_BRACES}` placeholders. No filled-in example data.

